edu.ucsb.cs56.projects.games.cs56_games_maze

Class MazeGameSave

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ucsb.cs56.projects.games.cs56_games_maze.MazeGameSave
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class MazeGameSave
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Serializable container for holding all necessary game state data. Used for both in-progress saves and end-of-game saves. In case of in-progress saves, saves player position and time elapsed. Always saves maze configuration and associated settings.
    Version:
    CS56 S13 UCSB
    Author:
    Evan West
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
